<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Game</title>
 
</head>

<body>
  <div class="row justify-space-between-md">
    <div>
      <h1  id="gameScore">Score: 0</h1>
      <hr><br>
      <h2 id="submittedWord"></h2>
      <p id="submittedWordDef"></p>
      <p id="gameStatus"></p>
      <hr><br>
      <h2 id="gameValues"></h2>

      <div>
        <input class="input" type="text" id="gameTextEntry" autocomplete="off"/>
        <button id="submitWord" type="button">Submit Word</button> <br>
        <h2 id="letterPool"></h2>
        <button id="newGame" type="button">Start a New Game</button>
        <button id="submitScore" type="button">Submit Score</button><br><br>
        <p>INSTRUCTIONS:</p>
        <p>Creating words gives you points for each letter used.</p> 
        <p>Getting down to 3 or fewer letters will refill your letters up to 12.</p>
        <p>Completely using up all 12 letters will result in an additional +5 points.</p>
        <p><i>Hint: Don't submit the first word you find, but type it out and then look to the </i></p>
        <p><i>letters that remain to make you still have letters you can make words out of.</i></p>
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="./js/gameLogic.js"></script>
</body>